structure.unit: ARTICLE LVI. MIAMI-DADE COUNTY CITIZENS TASK FORCE ON INCORPORATION

text.section:
Sec. 2-653. Report.
The task force shall submit a written report to the County Commission with its recommendations relating to subsections(1) and (3) hereof no later than February 28, 1994. The task force shall submit a written report to the County Commission with its recommendations relating to subsection(2) hereof no later than September 30, 1994.
